      "strategic_advice": "When you see prompts asking for an explanation, always push your answer to the very end.\n- Ask yourself **'and then what happens?'** to make sure you include the final consequence.\n- Use a **'so that...'** or **'causing...'** clause to connect your facts to the final result.",
