      "strategic_advice": "When you see special instruction words, treat them as stop signs.\n- **Circle or highlight** words like **'not'**, **'without'**, or **'only'** before you look at the options.\n- Double-check the exact wording (like **'populations'** vs individuals) to make sure you are answering exactly what is asked.",
      "trigger_keywords": [
